User Module – Functional Flow
	1.	Index Page
	•	Login (existing user)
	•	Register (new user → then login)
	2.	User Home Page
	•	Displays available books
	•	Navbar Options:
	•	🔍 Search Bar
	•	🎯 Filter Option
	•	🛒 Cart
	•	📦 Order Section
	•	👤 Profile Section
	3.	Cart Section
	•	View cart items
	•	Adjust quantity
	•	➡️ Proceed to Checkout Page
	•	Enter Shipping Address
	•	Choose Payment Method
	•	Make Payment
	•	✅ Order Placed & Confirmed
	4.	Order Section
	•	View all orders placed
	•	Cancel Orders
	•	Filter orders by:
	•	Order status (e.g., Confirmed, Delivered, Cancelled)
	•	Time period
	5.	Profile Section
	•	Edit profile details
	•	View all past orders
	•	Change password
	•	Logout




Admin Module – Functional Flow
	1.	Login Page
	•	Admin logs in using credentials
	2.	Admin Dashboard
	•	Overview:
	•	📦 Total Orders
	•	📚 Total Books in Stock
	•	🧑‍ Users (Active Users Count)
	•	💰 Total Revenue
	•	Highlights:
	•	🕒 Recent Orders
	•	🔥 Top Selling Books
	3.	Navigation Menu (Left/Top Panel)
	•	Dashboard (default home)
	•	Orders
	•	View all orders
	•	Change order status: Pending, Processing, Shipped, Delivered, Cancelled
	•	View individual order details
	•	Search & filter by date and status
	•	Order status counts: pending, shipped, delivered, cancelled, etc.
	•	Inventory
	•	View stock overview:
	•	Total book types
	•	Low stock / Out of stock / In-stock
	•	View stock per book
	•	Categories
	•	Add / Edit genres (categories)
	•	Books
	•	Add new books
	•	Edit or Delete existing books
	•	Logout
	•	Option: 🔄 Switch to User
